 Well, the two of us moved back permanently. 

13
00:00:56,600 --> 00:00:59,020
 We won’t leave again. 

14
00:01:00,280 --> 00:01:05,440
 Wow, my daughter's birthday will be a noisy one this year, right? 

15
00:01:06,050 --> 00:01:07,170
 Who said you can? 

16
00:01:07,170 --> 00:01:09,180
 I'm not glad to see either of you. 

17
00:01:09,180 --> 00:01:11,470
 I don't know what brought you here, 

18
00:01:11,470 --> 00:01:13,420
 but leave me out of your plans. 

19
00:01:13,420 --> 00:01:15,830
 She absolutely hates us. 

20
00:01:15,830 --> 00:01:18,320
 Hae Joon hurt his leg. 

21
00:01:18,320 --> 00:01:20,910
 Have you gone crazy? 

22
00:01:20,910 --> 00:01:22,560
 Where is it? 

23
00:01:22,560 --> 00:01:24,230
 Which leg? 

24
00:01:25,640 --> 00:01:28,590
 It's my fault. 

25
